## Ignore content inside minted / code environments
VerbEnvir { code minted }

## Suppress warnings:
##  4  — Italic correction (`\/') found in non-italic buffer
## 31  — This text may be ignored (closing brace in newenvironment)
## 36  — You should put a space in front of parenthesis
CmdLine { -n4 -n31 -n36 }
